266
01:17:51.669 --> 01:17:52.862
Vete.

267
01:17:57.304 --> 01:17:58.565
Gracias.

268
01:18:05.270 --> 01:18:06.463
Márchate.

269
01:18:22.305 --> 01:18:23.737
Ten cuidado.

270
01:18:31.739 --> 01:18:32.864
Vigila tu salud.

271
01:18:33.805 --> 01:18:35.533
