275
01:20:29.448 --> 01:20:30.698
Que tengas un buen viaje.

276
01:20:34.515 --> 01:20:35.844
Adiós.

277
01:20:48.483 --> 01:20:51.449
Tranquilo.

278
01:20:55.150 --> 01:20:56.548
Entra.

279
01:21:03.384 --> 01:21:04.679
Al aeropuerto.

280
01:21:23.652 --> 01:21:25.118
