283
01:21:37.553 --> 01:21:38.644
Subid chicos.

284
01:21:38.720 --> 01:21:39.878
Subamos entonces.

285
01:21:40.286 --> 01:21:41.410
Dame una vuelta.

286
01:21:41.652 --> 01:21:42.710
Gracias.

287
01:21:42.787 --> 01:21:43.811
Continua.

288
01:21:43.888 --> 01:21:44.888
Haz un intento.

289
01:21:45.321 --> 01:21:46.616
